  "excerpt": "This peaches and cream baked oatmeal is my modern twist on the classic favorite I used to eat growing up. It's super flavorful and satisfying, almost like oatmeal cake! Made with plain greek yogurt and maple syrup, it's dreamy and so easy to make.",
