-8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-8-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-8-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003ePeaches and Cream Baked Oatmeal\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"100196\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e40\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e55\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis peaches and cream baked oatmeal is my modern twist on the classic favorite I used to eat growing up. It\u0026#39;s super flavorful and satisfying, almost like oatmeal cake! Made with plain greek yogurt and maple syrup, it\u0026#39;s dreamy and so easy to make.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-100196-ingredients\" data-recipe=\"100196\" data-servings=\"12\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eold-fashioned rolled oats\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 ½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/ground-cinnamon-4-1oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77586380?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ecinnamon\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/clabber-girl-gluten-free-double-acting-baking-powder-8-1oz/-/A-14770673?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebaking powder\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/morton-coarse-kosher-salt-16oz/-/A-13170448?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ekosher salt\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/vital-farms-pasture-raised-grade-a-large-eggs-12ct/-/A-18783617?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003elarge eggs\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 ⅓\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/fage-total-5-milkfat-plain-greek-yogurt-32oz/-/A-46778312?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eplain greek yogurt\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/2-reduced-fat-milk-1gal-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-13276204?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003emilk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/100-pure-maple-syrup-12-fl-oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-78792428?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003emaple syrup\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/mccormick-pure-vanilla-extract-1oz/-/A-13353205?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003evanilla extract\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/mccormick-pure-almond-extract-2oz/-/A-53245136?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ealmond extract\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"10\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ediced peaches\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-100196-instructions\" data-recipe=\"100196\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100196-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreheat the oven to 350 degrees F. Spray a 9x13 inch baking dish with nonstick spray.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100196-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn a small bowl, whisk together the oats, cinnamon, baking powder and salt. In a large bowl, whisk together the eggs, yogurt, milk, maple syrup, vanilla extract and almond extract.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100196-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd the dry ingredients to the wet and mix until combined. Stir in the diced peaches. Spread the mixture into the baking dish.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100196-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn a bowl, mash together the sugar, flour, butter and cinnamon with a fork, combining the butter into the dry ingredients. Use your hands and continuously rub the mixture together until it resembles sand.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100196-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSprinkle the streusel all over the oats.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100196-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eBake for 35 to 40 minutes, or until it’s golden and set. Let cool slightly before serving. Serve with yogurt, a drizzle of heavy cream, extra peaches or whatever you wish.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBreakfast\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-20-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"peaches and cream baked oatmeal\" width=\"1718\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Peaches and Cream Baked Oatmeal.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-20-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-20-scaled.jpg 1718w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-20-728x932.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-20-768x983.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-20-1200x1536.jpg 1200w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-20-1599x2048.jpg 1599w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/peaches-and-cream-baked-oatmeal-20-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1718px) 100vw, 1718px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThat looks like dessert.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\u003c/article\u003e \n\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
